\begin_inset listings
inline false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

val f: [A, B] => A => (A => B) => B =
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

  [A, B] => (x: A) => (g: A => B) => g(x)
\end_layout

\end_inset

This syntax corresponds more closely to the mathematical notation shown
