\begin_layout Plain Layout

Int
\end_layout

\end_inset

, but we can never get a value of type 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

Nothing
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 So, regardless of the type 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

A
